title: (x) Swashy italic "Subscribe" and "Quick Post" - Monotype Corsiva {Dan Beltechi}
content:
I have this font somewhere on my computer. I've had it for years, but I can't remember which one it is and I've just spent a really long time typing them all out to see if I can figure it out only to fail miserably. You guys have always been so helpful in the past, so can anyone ID this font for me? Excuse the small graphics. This is the only size I have.

Thanks in advance.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100202075245im_/http:/typophile.com/files/subscribe_5249.gif)
  

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100202075245im_/http:/typophile.com/files/quick-post_5041.gif)
author: wyllomoon

comments.content: Ah, yes! That's it. Thank you very much.
